body_html: This appears to be a bug in Tensorflow 1.7; when I compiled with TF 1.6, everything worked as expected. The output of tensorflow::OpRegistry::Global()->DebugString(false) is identical, but no error is thrown when loading the model.

body: This appears to be a bug in Tensorflow 1.7; when I compiled with TF 1.6, everything worked as expected. The output of `tensorflow::OpRegistry::Global()->DebugString(false)` is identical, but no error is thrown when loading the model.
